whereas.text:
Whereas this event began over 30 years ago in France as Fête de la Musique, and observations of
			 Make Music Day now take place internationally in 800 cities in 110
			 countries around the world;

Whereas making music continues to demonstrate the power of music as providing enjoyment, building
			 cultural connections, raising social awareness, celebrating history, and
			 examining the whole of the human experience;
